config BR2_PACKAGE_YAWN
	bool "yawn"
	help
	  Yet Another Watchdog Nudger.
	  Minimal user space part of a watchdog implementation.
	  It activates the watchdog driver and then periodically kicks it,
	  to let it know the system is still operational.
	  If no kicks are received for a while, the driver resets the system.

	  https://github.com/Ayla-/yawn
